## Protocol

	Function	Client					Channel 			Server
	==================================================================
	join			----------------- connect ---------------->
	request			----------------- join ------------------->
					<---- status || challenge || start	-------
	
	start			----------------- announce --------------->
	session			<---------------- accept* -----------------
	
	save			----------------- store ------------------>
	history			<---------------- status ------------------
	
	load			----------------- restore ---------------->
	history			<---------------- status ------------------
	
	login			----------------- login ------------------>
	request			<----- status, remove*, accept* -----------
					
	relay			----------------- relay ------------------>
	message			<---------------- relay** -----------------
	
	* sends to all clients
	** sends to all clients except the requesting client
	
